7.40	Volksfront	Volksfront	Volksfront holds several events, including weekend-long white power concerts and speakers two or three times a year. The group also holds white unity gatherings and memorial parties in remembrance of white supremacists who have been murdered or imprisoned around the world. An annual Volksfront event called Althing is held south of St. Louis, Missouri at the group's Samuel Weaver Memorial Hall, which is named after the son of Randy Weaver, who was killed by federal agents in 1992.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/db/Volksfrontalt.jpg/220px-Volksfrontalt.jpg
